Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切开始于神木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.76,0:00:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断战斗\N不断祈求  不断寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中产生了强烈的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明的未来从现在开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.84,0:00:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要瞒着犬夜叉\N回到现代好好的放松一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.71,0:00:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我的同学\N由加  绘理  亚由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直说想要看看犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起了大骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导我们的最后一块碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯井的另一边\N战国的世界里还有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传说故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.19,0:00:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.35,0:00:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为谁而流的眼泪祈祷般地流下脸颊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.40,0:00:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隐藏脆弱  温柔地接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.07,0:00:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连呼吸都忘记  眼中的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.18,0:00:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有太阳闪耀着 不断寻找着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.08,0:01:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝视镜子 你一定能看见立誓的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.86,0:01:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的背后也有翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.93,0:01:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的改变  将改变世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.67,0:01:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现梦想的爱的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.14,0:01:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越虚幻的海市蜃楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.55,0:01:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空有光  大地有水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.39,0:01:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强的心灵带你到未来的ANGELUS（奉告祈祷）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.16,0:01:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双手握紧热情的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.35,0:02:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好在那边休息一阵子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要好好的静养一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次可是被老鼠\N咬得好惨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得要用药喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会带来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐还在世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像不是很惊讶的样子\N阿枫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.43,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两个像是式神的童子\N来过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走了有着姐姐骨灰的墓土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那些墓土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.11,0:03:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是为了治疗桔梗姐姐\N被奈落打伤的身体用的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道\N你有什么样的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得\N桔梗能够得救就是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.56,0:03:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救回中了奈落瘴气\N而倒下的桔梗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.84,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是戈薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第160话\N召唤幸福  脚踏两条船的暴力男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蚋  你好重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉正在做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没跟他说一声\N就自己跑回来现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.12,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然桔梗好像恢复了灵力\N精神好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她还是离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.13,0:05:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许犬夜叉心里\N其实还是很想追上去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.35,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回到了枫姥姥的村里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又好像有话难以启齿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.93,0:05:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我还是第二位候补吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么擅自让戈薇回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用不着每件事\N都得得到你的许可吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想回来这里\N把桔梗姑娘的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉枫姥姥的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就不好说话了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇是特地让你们好说话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又没说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.39,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有跟阿枫说什么\N戈薇不能听的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道又是我的错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.83,0:06:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来\N还是只有戈薇说的才有用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的咯  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一瞬间\N我还以为有用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度\N根本治不了这个家伙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居把旧的脚踏车送给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你不是说在那边\N把脚踏车弄丢了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这台好像有点生锈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好感动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  还不去学校吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要迟到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只要去了那边\N马上就会弄脏了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然让犬夜叉背着也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是不能没有这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  很完美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发亮耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬…犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没那么闲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  为什么不跟我打声招呼\N就这样跑回来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛突然冒出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把脚踏车弄坏了啦  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  都弄歪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐擦得好辛苦\N好不容易才让它闪闪发亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小事\N把它扳回原样不就好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.66,0:08:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我负责修好总行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再碰它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就在生气嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.83,0:08:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不像是已经算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.04,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.88,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早\N早安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是来干什么的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还一副脾气很大的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊\N真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加  绘理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  好像不太开心耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是上次你说的他\N又做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么老是猜得这么准啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.58,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还是老样子\N不良的男朋友脚踏两条船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还有很多不得已的原因\N所以也没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  脚踏两条船也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的还是没有办法\N决定哪一边咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.73,0:09:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要决定选择其中一个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚犬夜叉的心里面\N还想着桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定跟他在一起的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.61,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还是喜欢他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.15,0:09:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直觉得\N就算那样也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是无法决定还没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.95,0:09:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他心里已经定了第一位\N第二位那就惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一位  第二位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指喜欢的顺位吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话又说回来了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁排第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道真正的答案啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一位  第二位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说顺位的话\N我应该是排在第二位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也并不是说\N第二位就一定不好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是炖了第二次的汤\N更适合做味噌汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮出来的东西更好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是餐馆的调味\N第一次炖出的才是最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N在棒球里捕手是第二重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然处于指挥者的位置\N才是重点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有歌舞伎里的二枚目\N也是很帅的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.68,0:10:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都已经这样子了\N不见面是不是比较好  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是个方法喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没办法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙\N已经追到我们家里来了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一大早就跑来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你家啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.07,0:11:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.83,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇的不良男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话吃吃看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理得好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说\N这是从人家那里拿来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.56,0:11:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要代替之前\N在那边坏掉的那一辆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N是我们邻居送给我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…不好意思喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它弄坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不是在修理吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.01,0:11:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.79,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点东西  只要像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  为什么诸事不顺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手啊  可恶的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你有种  看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过才对付这一两个轮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会输啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会是怎样的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既任性又花心的暴力男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她们真的跟来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还叫我不要再跟他见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我看\N大家准备考试已经很忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做这种事的时候啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.59,0:13:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事比较重要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他让你这么痛苦\N我们得好好的念念他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.09,0:13:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你们这么说的话\N他会发飚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会发飚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人愈来愈讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要表达出我们的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的\N让她们见到犬夜叉就惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说他是半妖\N真面目曝光就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪犬夜叉不好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事没事就跑到这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看  戈薇还在烦恼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘理\N你刚才是不是说得太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许真的有点过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.36,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管他是什么样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是戈薇喜欢的人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该支持她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才算是朋友嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要担心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇\N我们绝对会站在你这边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他有多暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他再怎么花心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.56,0:14:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是铁车子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么比早上还要糟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这个被戈薇看到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赔偿她不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥你说的金刚石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种石头对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.25,0:14:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做钻石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个这种宝石\N可以买好几辆脚踏车呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以用铁碎牙\N随便劈把它劈出一堆来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿得出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚枪破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有金刚枪掉出来才对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再这样破坏下去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样的话如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我打到它掉出来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥说他想要打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赚足够的钱\N好赔偿弄坏的那辆脚踏车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很贵的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.83,0:16:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不让犬夜叉出来的话\N解释起来一定更麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇的背影\N看起来好像很苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到那个不良男友\N要先好好的夸夸他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他把前额的发际剃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算裤子是紫色\N或是粉红色都要这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.85,0:16:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前卫艺术吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.63,0:16:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.16,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她男朋友的名字吗\N你在哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是队名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是什么洋基队的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这个放这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后换这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个箱子是放这边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇好像在叫你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听错了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那个壶放到这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要摔坏喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我们代代相传\N来历不小的壶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗  千万要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仓库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.79,0:17:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  犬夜叉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N什么东西都被他破坏光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像已经回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是满怀期待来看他的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.12,0:18:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他应该经常会来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这也不一定啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.93,0:18:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来帮忙拿茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.80,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们慢慢坐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜  好想看看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  我们都专程来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.92,0:18:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你\N你从一大早就生什么气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说不定就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是戏剧公演的时候\N闯进来搅局的那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭的时候\N跟北条同学决斗的那个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你就是戈薇的男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候是戈薇叫你来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么犬夜叉会在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖的身份要曝露啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从什么时候开始\N跟戈薇交往的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很久了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的和服\N是在神社打工穿的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你眼睛的颜色很特别耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发颜色是染的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少见的颜色耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.88,0:19:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸摸看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以\N不过你们也真是奇怪的家伙耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聊得还挺好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想他是不是混血儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混血?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  是这样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他是半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.50,0:20:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人嫉妒  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有在国外生活过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候来这里的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  bye-bye
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.22,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇\N他没你说的那么糟糕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他是个穿着特攻服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个没有眉毛的男生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.86,0:20:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛  他是有点不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们原来想象的完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相处喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题只剩下北条同学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还不知道这个男的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.28,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…她们是在赞美犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.82,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然犬夜叉看起来就是很有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…就不要了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.24,0:21:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那台铁车子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那个\N以后我来背你就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说  爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.58,0:21:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥告诉我\N可以用铁碎牙弄出钻石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.22,0:21:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就让他赔你就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.32,0:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一块  两块  三块  不够啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信对不对  爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈那边我去道歉就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不生气啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.24,0:21:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像觉得\N现在什么事都没那么糟啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.39,0:22:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New World 全新梦想的起点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.16,0:22:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向目标持续旅程 直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.37,0:22:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brand-New Mind 怀抱热情直到下一扇门扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.64,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向未知的世界 快奔驰吧
